1
00:00:00,587 --> 00:00:08,687
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,862 --> 00:00:17,099
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,337 --> 00:00:19,328
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,342 --> 00:00:26,108
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,179 --> 00:00:29,546
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,749 --> 00:00:33,310
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,686 --> 00:00:37,053
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,123 --> 00:00:44,552
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,631 --> 00:00:53,767
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,840 --> 00:01:01,872
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,115 --> 00:01:08,953
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:09,022 --> 00:01:17,088
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,397 --> 00:01:25,862
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,939 --> 00:01:27,964
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:47,196
Master Jiraiya... I believe in you.

16
00:02:04,655 --> 00:02:10,491
<i>The Summoning Jutsu.</i>
<i>Wisdom of the Toad Sage!</i>

17
00:02:38,722 --> 00:02:40,121
Well well...

18
00:02:41,458 --> 00:02:43,517
You don't sleep at all?

19
00:02:45,429 --> 00:02:46,919
What do you want?

20
00:02:47,898 --> 00:02:51,026
I thought I'd crush you now.

21
00:02:52,236 --> 00:02:56,036
If I do that,
there'd be the possibility for me,

22
00:02:56,106 --> 00:02:59,769
after the first battle,
to be able to fight Sasuke.

23
00:03:00,644 --> 00:03:04,045
I know your Sand attack.

24
00:03:04,849 --> 00:03:08,876
I wonder which is faster,
yours or my Sound.

25
00:03:27,304 --> 00:03:28,601
In the full moon...

26
00:03:30,207 --> 00:03:34,041
in the full moon, his blood boils.

27
00:03:45,556 --> 00:03:48,616
W-What the heck... are you?

28
00:04:20,925 --> 00:04:24,554
Amazing... So that's his true form?

29
00:04:25,996 --> 00:04:29,727
But... is it okay?
He's a Sound Ninja...

30
00:04:30,367 --> 00:04:34,098
It's all right.
He's long since served his purpose.

31
00:04:34,939 --> 00:04:37,772
I thought he was a guinea pig
in order to see...

32
00:04:38,442 --> 00:04:40,808
the power of the boy
called Sasuke or something...

33
00:04:43,714 --> 00:04:45,978
<i>Why...is he with the Sand Ninja?</i>

34
00:04:47,084 --> 00:04:50,076
No, that's not necessary anymore...

35
00:04:50,421 --> 00:04:54,824
Actually, I'd already been ordered
to seize Sasuke.

36
00:04:54,892 --> 00:04:57,292
But I failed...

37
00:04:58,162 --> 00:04:59,026
What did you say?

38
00:04:59,096 --> 00:04:59,892
That's right.

39
00:05:00,464 --> 00:05:01,988
<i>...for the likes of you?</i>

40
00:05:03,033 --> 00:05:05,331
<i>Are you looking to take me on?</i>

41
00:05:05,836 --> 00:05:12,241
<i>You willful little brat...</i>
<i>Don't mess around with grown ups.</i>

42
00:05:12,943 --> 00:05:18,882
<i>Don't be so arrogant.</i>
<i>The situation is in my favor.</i>

43
00:05:25,923 --> 00:05:29,689
It's also been found out that
I'm a minion of the Sound.

44
00:05:31,061 --> 00:05:36,761
Then... if they find out that you're
having a secret meeting here with me...

45
00:05:37,568 --> 00:05:41,436
the plan to destroy the Leaf Village
and everything will be for naught!

46
00:05:43,007 --> 00:05:46,465
I heard...
that you're Orochimaru's right hand man.

47
00:05:47,077 --> 00:05:51,013
Being revealed to them and coming
nonchalantly to meet with me...

48
00:05:51,648 --> 00:05:53,240
You must be a fool.

49
00:05:54,885 --> 00:05:59,447
Well... to be exact, my true identity
wasn't found out...

50
00:06:00,391 --> 00:06:02,256
I let them find out.

51
00:06:04,461 --> 00:06:08,022
I wanted to see how far
the Leaf Village would go...

52
00:06:09,366 --> 00:06:12,233
Even after that it wouldn't
be too late to seize Sasuke.

53
00:06:12,936 --> 00:06:16,531
If you guys are going to fail,
we'll back off immediately...

54
00:06:17,174 --> 00:06:20,337
It's a plan that was originally
posed by the Sound, so.

55
00:06:24,148 --> 00:06:26,378
The Sand is invisible until
the last moment.

56
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:29,748
This is the will of the Kazekage.

57
00:06:30,554 --> 00:06:31,748
<i>Holy smokes...</i>

58
00:06:32,689 --> 00:06:33,986
That's fine.

59
00:06:34,925 --> 00:06:37,553
This is the carry out plan from Sound.

60
00:06:38,128 --> 00:06:38,685
Okay.

61
00:06:40,297 --> 00:06:45,599
And please... tell them about
this plan soon.

62
00:06:46,703 --> 00:06:47,397
Yeah.

63
00:06:48,739 --> 00:06:49,728
I know.

64
00:06:51,742 --> 00:06:54,108
Okay, I'll be going.

65
00:06:54,711 --> 00:06:56,702
<i>To think our allied nation,</i>
<i>the Village Hidden in the Sand,</i>

66
00:06:56,980 --> 00:06:59,005
<i>has been already associated</i>
<i>with the Sound...?!</i>

67
00:07:00,017 --> 00:07:01,780
<i>I must tell Lord Hokage about this quick.</i>

68
00:07:02,186 --> 00:07:03,585
Oh, by the way...

69
00:07:05,556 --> 00:07:07,854
I'll take care of the clean up.

70
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,460
No, I'll do it...

71
00:07:11,995 --> 00:07:14,463
As the member of Sand Village
of the Land of Wind,

72
00:07:14,531 --> 00:07:17,967
I must do what I can for my allies...

73
00:07:18,902 --> 00:07:22,065
Besides... it's just one mouse.

74
00:07:23,006 --> 00:07:24,132
It'll be easy.

75
00:07:40,023 --> 00:07:43,220
Well well, it's Mr. Proctor.

76
00:07:45,329 --> 00:07:48,992
What in the world are you
doing here alone?

77
00:07:50,734 --> 00:07:52,361
It seems I have no choice,
but to fight.

78
00:08:20,230 --> 00:08:21,254
Leaf Style...

79
00:08:21,331 --> 00:08:22,628
Crescent Moon Dance!

80
00:08:41,985 --> 00:08:42,952
<i>I can't pull it out.</i>

81
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:47,488
This technique is...
the Leaf Style Crescent Moon Dance.

82
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:50,017
Being able to manage it
at such a young age.

83
00:08:50,727 --> 00:08:53,719
As expected,
this village is full of talented Ninja.

84
00:08:56,133 --> 00:08:57,657
Your talent with a sword is superb.

85
00:08:58,035 --> 00:09:02,972
But, a real sword with substance
can be stopped.

86
00:09:03,473 --> 00:09:09,139
However... a Wind sword can't
be stopped by anyone.

87
00:09:21,391 --> 00:09:21,982
Take that!

88
00:09:23,393 --> 00:09:24,553
That does it!

89
00:09:33,337 --> 00:09:35,202
Nice, nice.

90
00:09:36,907 --> 00:09:37,737
Hey...

91
00:09:38,775 --> 00:09:40,800
This is paradise.

92
00:09:42,479 --> 00:09:44,174
Hey, I said.

93
00:09:57,694 --> 00:10:00,925
Isn't it time for you to turn
this way already?

94
00:10:01,398 --> 00:10:06,859
If you join my training,
I'll give you lots of "service."

95
00:10:07,638 --> 00:10:09,663
P-l-e-a-s-e.

96
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:14,434
So you finally came out...
I was waiting for you.

97
00:10:17,881 --> 00:10:18,506
What?!

98
00:10:22,653 --> 00:10:26,111
Are you making fun of me?

99
00:10:26,723 --> 00:10:29,214
Right back at you.

100
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,393
I'm hungry.

101
00:10:31,561 --> 00:10:33,324
Let's get back to the inn.

102
00:10:35,532 --> 00:10:38,228
Owww, darn it!

103
00:10:40,604 --> 00:10:44,165
Okay... I'll teach you a technique.

104
00:10:45,275 --> 00:10:48,142
Do you really mean that?

105
00:10:50,714 --> 00:10:55,151
Do you remember what I told you
yesterday about the two types of Chakra?

106
00:10:55,619 --> 00:10:57,644
Huh? Yesterday's talk?

107
00:10:57,888 --> 00:11:02,848
You know, what you said about blue
and red Chakra or something.

108
00:11:03,126 --> 00:11:05,617
Oh... What about it?

109
00:11:05,996 --> 00:11:10,262
You said that when a great power
came out, you felt red Chakra.

110
00:11:10,634 --> 00:11:13,364
Yeah, it was like that.

111
00:11:13,603 --> 00:11:17,095
Try building up that red Chakra right now.

112
00:11:17,341 --> 00:11:21,038
Hmm. Even you say so...

113
00:11:21,545 --> 00:11:23,240
I'll give it a try, but...

114
00:11:34,991 --> 00:11:35,958
How about it?

115
00:11:36,026 --> 00:11:38,722
Hmm, it's not right.

116
00:11:39,029 --> 00:11:40,894
It's the same Chakra as always.

117
00:11:41,264 --> 00:11:44,825
Jeez, you have no talent.

118
00:11:45,969 --> 00:11:47,903
Don't be talking all high and mighty!

119
00:11:47,971 --> 00:11:48,869
In the first place,

120
00:11:48,939 --> 00:11:52,375
I really don't understand those
two types of Chakra myself!

121
00:11:52,909 --> 00:11:54,968
Just keep trying.

122
00:12:01,118 --> 00:12:05,054
<i>Humph... So he doesn't understand it...</i>
<i>himself, eh.</i>

123
00:12:06,390 --> 00:12:08,187
<i>It seems Naruto himself still hasn't</i>
<i>realized that</i>

124
00:12:08,258 --> 00:12:12,991
<i>the red Chakra is</i>
<i>the Nine Tailed Fox's Chakra.</i>

125
00:12:17,934 --> 00:12:20,835
<i>Well, guessing from his story...</i>

126
00:12:21,405 --> 00:12:24,374
<i>it seems the excitement of danger</i>
<i>and heightened emotion</i>

127
00:12:24,441 --> 00:12:27,308
<i>are the key to summon</i>
<i>the Nine Tailed Fox Chakra.</i>

128
00:12:28,378 --> 00:12:30,005
No good, not good,

129
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,708
Only the usual Chakra's coming out.

130
00:12:33,183 --> 00:12:34,707
Say, Pervy Sage...

131
00:12:34,785 --> 00:12:39,017
What the heck does the red Chakra and
the technique you're going to teach me

132
00:12:39,089 --> 00:12:41,182
have to do with each other?

133
00:12:41,291 --> 00:12:42,690
Listen, boy.

134
00:12:44,961 --> 00:12:46,588
For the technique
I'm about to teach you,

135
00:12:46,663 --> 00:12:50,224
the Chakra you've had until now
is not nearly enough.

136
00:12:51,735 --> 00:12:56,399
Therefore, you'll have to able to
pull out and use the "other" Chakra

137
00:12:56,473 --> 00:13:00,500
that has been dormant within
you at any time you need.

138
00:13:01,511 --> 00:13:07,006
But how do you know that
I have such a Chakra?

139
00:13:07,684 --> 00:13:09,914
Oh, just what I wanted to hear.

140
00:13:10,821 --> 00:13:12,254
Actually...

141
00:13:13,023 --> 00:13:15,389
it's because I'm a sage.

142
00:13:15,892 --> 00:13:19,191
Jeez... that's no answer.

143
00:13:19,563 --> 00:13:22,361
Anyway, the special Chakra
that only you have

144
00:13:22,432 --> 00:13:24,798
will become your greatest weapon.

145
00:13:25,101 --> 00:13:26,864
Greatest weapon?

146
00:13:28,338 --> 00:13:31,774
Not using that is like wasting treasure.

147
00:13:32,175 --> 00:13:35,372
There's no need to forcedly do
the same training as everyone else.

148
00:13:36,012 --> 00:13:37,980
Everyone has what they're good at
and poor at.

149
00:13:39,449 --> 00:13:41,940
You have your own style.

150
00:13:43,086 --> 00:13:48,581
Your training until now, maintaining
and releasing a set amount of Chakra,

151
00:13:48,658 --> 00:13:50,023
was in other words,

152
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:54,426
training to control the suppression of
Chakra so that you wouldn't get exhausted.

153
00:13:55,265 --> 00:13:57,392
But you who have a lot of stamina

154
00:13:57,467 --> 00:13:59,196
should be about power rather
than a cheap trick.

155
00:14:03,507 --> 00:14:06,499
You, who has two types of Chakra
and doesn't exhaust easily,

156
00:14:06,576 --> 00:14:09,739
should release the largest amount
of Chakra you can

157
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:14,249
and train to increase the absolute amount
of Chakra that you can use.

158
00:14:15,252 --> 00:14:18,847
Then there are tons of Jutsu
and techniques you can use.

159
00:14:20,123 --> 00:14:22,523
What, for example?

160
00:14:23,059 --> 00:14:29,123
For example... summoning jutsu
that I'm going to teach you now.

161
00:14:32,903 --> 00:14:34,063
Summoning?

162
00:14:34,504 --> 00:14:35,368
Right.

163
00:14:39,009 --> 00:14:41,739
It's a type of spatio temporal technique

164
00:14:41,811 --> 00:14:45,247
where you sign a contract in blood
with all kinds of living creatures

165
00:14:45,315 --> 00:14:47,215
and summon whenever you like
with Ninjutsu.

166
00:14:49,619 --> 00:14:54,579
Oh! That sounds awesome.
Teach me quick!

167
00:14:55,492 --> 00:14:57,960
Before that...

168
00:14:58,228 --> 00:15:02,562
first, it's necessary to
use up all of your usual Chakra.

169
00:15:03,066 --> 00:15:04,590
Okay!

170
00:15:06,469 --> 00:15:07,766
Leave it to me.

171
00:15:13,376 --> 00:15:17,039
Well... So you can use the
Shadow Clone Jutsu.

172
00:15:17,347 --> 00:15:22,250
I have a good idea how to get rid
of my Chakra quickly.

173
00:15:37,167 --> 00:15:40,967
Well, you've multiplied quite a bit.

174
00:15:42,539 --> 00:15:46,532
Listen up. We're going to have
a battle royal now.

175
00:15:46,977 --> 00:15:50,071
The last one left will be
the strongest me...

176
00:15:50,513 --> 00:15:53,380
We're going to determine
the me among me!

177
00:15:53,817 --> 00:15:55,045
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

178
00:15:55,385 --> 00:15:59,788
I see.
Good thinking considering he's stupid.

179
00:16:00,357 --> 00:16:02,484
Okay, let's go!

180
00:16:27,384 --> 00:16:31,218
My, this is a sexually unattractive scene.

181
00:16:59,516 --> 00:17:02,576
The finale is near at last.

182
00:17:32,449 --> 00:17:33,677
Well done.

183
00:17:41,191 --> 00:17:45,821
Sure enough, I'm the strongest me.

184
00:17:58,808 --> 00:18:02,608
It looks like you've finally used up
almost all of your Chakra.

185
00:18:05,448 --> 00:18:07,780
Now, at last I'll teach you
the technique.

186
00:18:09,319 --> 00:18:10,377
Oh, I've been waiting!

187
00:18:10,820 --> 00:18:13,755
First, I'll show you.

188
00:18:14,290 --> 00:18:15,780
Watch carefully.

189
00:18:19,696 --> 00:18:21,857
Summoning Jutsu!

190
00:18:28,104 --> 00:18:31,972
Ooh, so cool.

191
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:46,120
Open that scroll.

192
00:18:47,123 --> 00:18:49,785
It's a contract with the
summoning toads

193
00:18:49,859 --> 00:18:52,191
that I've taken over from generations.

194
00:18:53,296 --> 00:18:54,854
Sign your name in your own blood

195
00:18:55,365 --> 00:18:59,324
and stamp the fingerprints of one hand
in blood under that.

196
00:19:00,637 --> 00:19:04,300
Then build up Chakra in the place
you want to summon

197
00:19:04,374 --> 00:19:06,501
and set down the hand you contracted.

198
00:19:07,577 --> 00:19:11,138
The Sign is
Boar-Dog-Bird-Monkey-Sheep.

199
00:19:15,652 --> 00:19:22,114
NARUTO UZUMAKI.

200
00:19:33,002 --> 00:19:36,028
Okay... This is fine, right?

201
00:19:37,040 --> 00:19:41,568
It's easier for you to release
red Chakra right now.

202
00:19:42,445 --> 00:19:43,742
So give it a try.

203
00:19:44,147 --> 00:19:45,705
I already am.

204
00:19:46,516 --> 00:19:49,974
Boar, Dog, Bird, Monkey, Sheep.

205
00:19:51,054 --> 00:19:53,545
Ninja Art! Summoning jutsu.

206
00:20:14,978 --> 00:20:17,344
<i>A tadpole...</i>

207
00:20:18,147 --> 00:20:21,480
<i>This kid...has no talent, after all.</i>

208
00:20:49,512 --> 00:20:53,881
Hayate... what in the world happened?

209
00:21:13,337 --> 00:21:16,704
<i>One! First, Tyson jumps and slamdunks</i>

210
00:21:16,773 --> 00:21:20,106
<i>Two! He kisses and hugs everyone</i>
<i>randomly and says "I LOVE YOU"</i>

211
00:21:20,177 --> 00:21:23,613
<i>Three! Masala masters Yoga</i>
<i>but hates curry</i>

212
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:26,911
<i>Four! Sanchez is a lousy bullfighter. Ole!</i>

213
