<i>All over the world, the sky's smiling,</i>
<i>so look up and smile too</i>

214
00:21:33,423 --> 00:21:40,659
<i>Oh yeah! Oh yeah! Oh yeah!</i>
<i>Fight! Fight! Fight!</i>

215
00:21:51,041 --> 00:21:54,477
<i>One! Bodimahattaya san devotes</i>
<i>his time for digging black ships</i>

216
00:21:54,545 --> 00:21:57,844
<i>Two! Peking Duck, Action Scene,</i>
<i>Chen Lee speeds around on his bike</i>

217
00:21:57,915 --> 00:22:01,214
<i>Three! Popo loves to polish his Coteka</i>

218
00:22:01,285 --> 00:22:04,550
<i>Four! Japanese people,</i>
<i>now lend me you hand!</i>

219
00:22:04,755 --> 00:22:10,785
<i>All over the world, the sky's smiling,</i>
<i>so look up and smile too</i>

220
00:22:10,861 --> 00:22:18,199
<i>Oh yeah! Oh yeah! Oh yeah!</i>
<i>Fight! Fight! Fight!</i>

221
00:22:18,302 --> 00:22:24,730
<i>All over the world, the sky's smiling,</i>
<i>so look up and smile too</i>

222
00:22:24,808 --> 00:22:31,976
<i>Oh yeah! Oh yeah! Oh yeah!</i>
<i>Fight! Fight! Fight!</i>

223
00:22:38,256 --> 00:22:42,590
Ino! When I was going to visit
Sasuke at the hospital by myself...

224
00:22:42,660 --> 00:22:44,787
why are you coming along?

225
00:22:45,263 --> 00:22:46,992
Besides, what is that flower all about?

226
00:22:47,198 --> 00:22:49,962
A "rose for love"?
That's so lame.

227
00:22:50,401 --> 00:22:56,567
I chose this daffodil for him,
hoping Sasuke will get better soon.

228
00:22:57,542 --> 00:23:01,069
Next time, "A Feeling of Yearning,
A Flower Full of Hope"

229
00:23:01,245 --> 00:23:03,304
Cha! This is it!
